# Title: RDP Login from Localhost
# Author: Thomas Patzke
# Date: 2019-01-28
# Level: high
# Description: RDP login with localhost source address may be a tunnelled login
# MITRE Tactic: Lateral Movement
# Tags: attack.lateral-movement, car.2013-07-002, attack.t1021.001
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules/windows/builtin/security/account_management/win_security_rdp_localhost_login.yml

EventID=4624 IpAddress IN ("::1", "127.0.0.1") LogonType=10